               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this text, we will delve deeper into concepts of evolution and sums learned in previous games (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>). In addition, we will also reinforce knowledge from previous texts on multiplication (<htcite3>; <htcite4>). Therefore, we recommend playing the games and studying the texts before proceeding.",
